          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1483.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>, <strong>cider vinegar </strong>and <strong>onion marmalade</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>mustard & onion dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1483.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1483.-step-5-x400.jpg",
